name: Sage Mastery Slate
description: Struck to recognize your achievement in reaching the rank of 25 - Sage.

languages.description: Geschaffen, um dein Erreichen von Rang 25 - Weiser zu ehren.
languages.name: Meisterschaft-Insignie: Weiser

languages.description: Gravée pour commémorer votre réussite en atteignant le Palier 25 - Sage.
languages.name: Ardoise de Maîtrise - Sage

languages.description: Coniata per riconoscere il tuo successo nel raggiungere il grado 25 - Saggio.
languages.name: Targa Maestria - Saggio

languages.description: 랭크 25 - 세이지에 도달한 업적을 기리기 위한 표창패입니다.
languages.name: 세이지 마스터리 슬레이트

languages.description: Impresionado por reconocer tu logro al alcanzar el rango 25 - Sabio.
languages.name: Placa de Maestría de Sabio

languages.description: 为表彰你成功达到段位 25－圣者所打造的物品。
languages.name: 圣者精通石板

languages.description: セージ「マスタリーランク25」へ到達したテンノの成果を示す表彰楯。
languages.name: セージ マスタリー 表彰楯

languages.description: Stworzona, by upamiętnić Twój wyczyn w osiągnięciu rangi 25 - Mędrzec.
languages.name: Tablica Mistrzostwa Mędrzec

languages.description: Concedida em reconhecimento à sua conquista por alcançar o nível 25 - Sábio.
languages.name: Ardósia de Maestria: Sábio

languages.description: 篆刻來認可你達成精通段位 25－聖者的成就。

languages.description: ประทับตรารับรู้ถึงความสำเร็จของคุณในการไปถึงอันดับ 25 - ปราชญ์
languages.name: กระดานชนวนความเชี่ยวชาญ: ปราชญ์

languages.description: Seviye 25 - Sage seviyesine ulaşma başarını anmak için oluşturulmuştur.
languages.name: Sage Ustalık Plaketi
